line_1: Virtue consists in nudity of Breech!
line_2: With pikes and guns this moral dogma teach —

line_1: By the merit of running long nails in his breech.
line_2: No. His holiness rose to this sovereign pitch

line_1: But how many nails do you run in your breech?
line_2: I give to the poor, and I lend to the rich —
